				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/02/08/12511-les-10-mesures-qui-sauveraient-la-france-mais-qui-ne-seront-jamais-appliquees/comment-page-2?replytocom=62489#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-62489", "62489", "respond", "12511")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
